text: Summary Live Reporting By Anwen Lewis and Alun Jones All times stated are UK UpdateBore da Posted at 08:53 The Environment and Sustainability will start at 9am with the Minister for Natural Resources Carl Sargeant giving evidence. Mr Sargeant has previously described Wales as the " Real Madrid of Europe in terms of recycling " . After Wales rounded off their successful Euro 2016 campaign with a 2-0 win over Andorra last night, let's see if Mr Sargeant uses another football analogy this morning. ShareShare this post on
